00:29:10,430 --> 00:29:11,630
Adik kandungmu?

509
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:13,390
Ya.

510
00:29:14,380 --> 00:29:15,380
Baiklah...

511
00:29:16,430 --> 00:29:17,360
Aku tidak bisa membiarkan dia mengetahuinya
Aku tidak mengikuti kelas seni hari ini.

512
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:18,020
Hei!

513
00:29:18,980 --> 00:29:19,880
Apa yang kamu lakukan?

514
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:21,740
Kalian berdua tidak mirip.

515
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:22,300
Pokoknya,

516
00:29:22,330 --> 00:29:23,390
rahasiakan ini
dari yang lain.

517
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:25,190
Saya bisa merahasiakannya.

518
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,570
Tapi apa yang Anda tawarkan sebagai imbalannya?

519
00:29:27,970 --> 00:29:29,900
Hah?

520
00:29:37,710 --> 00:29:38,910
[Selalu Bertemu Lagi] [[n]]

521
00:29:44,010 --> 00:29:45,870
But what do you offer in exchange?

522
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,220
Huh?

523
00:30:59,990 --> 00:31:04,120
[Always Meet Again]

